      "writtenOn": "2021-01-14T19:43:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e I do see upside in delete, as it makes it easy to wipe out old data from Datastore.\n\nTrue, it does make things easier. I think the reason I choose write empty and lazy deletion in the future over immediate deletion is to follow this best practice for deletion[1] (i.e. Avoid deleting large numbers of entities across a small range of keys.) because CV is likely create/delete lease on a small range of AssetID (change number is monotonically increasing). But I\u0027m not sure if it is large enough concern to choose not to delete.\n\n[1]: https://cloud.google.com/datastore/docs/best-practices",
      "parentUuid": "def7b218_538f082b",
